title: Conshvi Men's Slim Fit Stretch Jeans Distressed Patchwork Stacked Frayed Straight Leg Skinny Denim Pants
description: MATERIAL: Mens slim fit straight leg jeans made of 90% Cotton, 10% Polyester comfy denim fabric. Skin-friendly and lightweight, skinny jeans can offer you maximum comfort and keep you relaxed for all day.
FASHION DESIGN: Men's skinny jeans with frayed tassels design at the seams. Zipper closure, Mid rise, 4 pockets, stacked patchwork slim fit denim pants.

ELEVATE YOUR STYLE: Fashion Y2K streetwear style design. Stacked jeans trendy design with appropriate cutting techniques,extremely showcasing your perfect leg shape. Easy to match with basic t-shirt, sweater, coat, jacket, creating a fashionable effect for you.

OCCASIONS: This slim fit cowboy denim pants are a must-have travel item in your wardrobe. The distressed washed looks cool and fit for daily wear, outfit wear like moto cycling, vacation, dating, or other occasions.
CARE WASH: Men's slim fit stretch jeans machine wash separately in cool water, do not bleach, tumble dry low.
